author: Samuel Lovett, Samuel Lovett
title: Coronavirus: US officials knew of Wuhan health crisis in November, a second report claims
description: Repeated warnings made to White House throughout December, says US media
content:
A second report has claimed that the US collected intelligence pointing to a public health crisis in Wuhan as far back as November, after officials dismissed allegations earlier this week.
